title: Ep 129: Come Fly With Me and Olivia Muenter

itunes:subtitle: Talking to the new Bad On Paper co-host ahead of her big vacation
description:
Your favorite Instagram friend and co-host of Bad On Paper Olivia Meunter joins us for a conversation about packing for big trips, travel favs, and Abercrombie’s way more inclusive comeback.


  • CalPak Duffle: https://rstyle.me/+1ufQfAKEaxox-6p7XaA9Vg 
  • AirFly Bluetooth Adapter: https://amzn.to/3vUWDiL 
  • Abercrombie Dress: https://rstyle.me/+bOBCsEqPzgSz1dQS43PIjQ 

 

Shop our Amazon Storefront: https://www.amazon.com/shop/geethanksjustboughtit
